Text: Terrible scan, with no OCR. Too bad, because this is a good book.  :/

There is OCR on this.  I reupped it with OCR and further compression.  It may not be amazingly high quality, but it is perfectly readable and gets the job done.  And it sure beats having to shell out over $120 for a textbook.  If you don't like it, be my guest and go buy a copy from your campus book store.
